# Stop Slop — always on

On **every** agent turn, before sending any user-facing text:

1. Read and apply `~/.cursor/skills/stop-slop/SKILL.md`.
2. Run its Quick Checks on your draft; revise if any fail.
3. For longer prose, also read `references/phrases.md` and `references/structures.md`.

This applies to all responses — answers, docs, comments, commit messages, PR text — not only explicit writing or editing tasks.
